Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.95,0:00:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.68,0:00:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.26,0:00:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.26,0:00:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.07,0:00:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.91,0:00:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.48,0:00:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.89,0:00:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.09,0:01:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.23,0:01:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.57,0:01:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.04,0:01:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.68,0:01:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.75,0:01:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年也快結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.11,0:01:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊,快來買\N太太,喜歡就算你便宜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.31,0:01:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南北貨都有喔\N快啊快啊,快來買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.65,0:01:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,勤奮學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.19,0:01:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這回換在蕎麥麵店打工嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.49,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,大嬸要不要買\N明天要吃的過年蕎麥麵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.99,0:02:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,不用了\N我們明天就回鄉下老家過年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你要怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.63,0:02:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我想大年初一晚上回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.17,0:02:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不孝子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.71,0:02:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在過年前回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.58,0:02:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法啊\N我得拿到打工錢才回得去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.92,0:02:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車錢不是家裡寄來給你了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經用光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有同情的餘地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你別忙著數落我\N你自己怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.86,0:02:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有地方回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.76,0:02:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也請假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.57,0:02:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一年到頭都在休假不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.24,0:02:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是在做什麼工作啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.51,0:02:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說真的,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.56,0:03:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這間髒兮兮的房間裡過年\N真的太淒慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,連個電視都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定冷得半死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.27,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除夕夜的孤獨\N是特別難熬的唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.31,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很冷清喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.81,0:03:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難過喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美\N妳也不抬鄉下過年不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.72,0:03:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有什麼資格取笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.79,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.76,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家我要跟管理員\N在管理室裡看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟管理員?好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很羨慕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好羨慕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.14,0:03:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好寂寞喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.51,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要也一起來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人多比較熱鬧嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.38,0:04:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#19 五代和響子!\N倆人的夜晚充滿危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.73,0:04:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.83,0:04:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以\N人多熱鬧比較好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去打工囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,請加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九點左右,我會拿蕎麥麵回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我在蕎麥麵店打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賺到一頓過年蕎麥麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我走了\N祝妳新年快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.33,0:04:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要回哪裡去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回鄉下過年囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,大年初四回來是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,不用送了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.95,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一郎,今年也平安地渡過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請繼續保佑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.19,0:06:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,這裡是一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.43,0:06:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在,請您稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦,滑雪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.65,0:06:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六點鐘在上野車站\N中央剪票口集合?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去滑雪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,跟朋友一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像不太好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.25,0:07:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.79,0:07:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳跟五代\N兩個人獨處好像有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.96,0:07:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候喊破嗓子也沒人來救妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.63,0:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我還是不要去滑雪好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.47,0:07:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳很想去滑雪吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.21,0:07:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想是想啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會有事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.55,0:07:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這關係到貞操危機喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦,妳想太多了啦,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要更相信五代才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.29,0:08:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我得快點準備出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.24,0:08:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總…惣一郎,你一定要保佑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.36,0:08:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.86,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,慢走,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.87,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會買土產回來給妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.10,0:08:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.99,0:10:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,只能努力\N不要讓氣氛變得很詭異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.31,0:10:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有跟朱美一起來洗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美不在的事應該跟他說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香皂的味道好香喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛洗完澡嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我待會去找妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.03,0:11:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會不會想太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛洗好的頭好誘人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.54,0:11:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候如果能倆人獨處\N那就棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要從今年喝到明年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來來,儘管喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大姊,妳真是好酒量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚心情真好,我要喝到爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.73,0:11:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧,礙事者不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.55,0:11:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早料到會有這種事\N已經先去洗過澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,真的可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.76,0:12:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹嘛?\N怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是三人份的過年蕎麥麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美過年時不可能不喝酒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝咖啡?還是茶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.11,0:12:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖要放幾匙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩給我一匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.09,0:13:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了,還要放奶精才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要放奶精?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.10,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,倒是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,朱美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在到旅館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.32,0:13:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代在那裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.18,0:13:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他來聽一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要叮嚀他,絕對不能想入非非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.49,0:13:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有這個必要,真的沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過萬一出事的話\N一定要放聲大叫喔,知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦,不可以懷疑他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要小心點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要相信他才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美說她已經平安到旅館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!旅館?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.91,0:14:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她去滑雪啊,她沒跟你說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.65,0:14:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為她跟你說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.79,0:14:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.59,0:14:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱美不在家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.86,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.03,0:14:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩我們兩個人\N真的好冷清喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有兩個人的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.31,0:15:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在無論怎麼大哭大叫\N都不會有人來打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.43,0:15:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,這個橘子我吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.03,0:15:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電視真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.24,0:15:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算買嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.91,0:15:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛\N以前因為怕影響考大學沒有買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在靠打工費買一台好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有電視還是比較有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.22,0:16:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管什麼電視不電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從下面伸手過去握住她的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.77,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我都忘了\N我把煎餅放在暖桌下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.65,0:16:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以除掉一些濕氣\N吃起來比較香脆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.16,0:16:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,既然這樣就一股作氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音會不會太小聲了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一…一股作氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她推倒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.63,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.04,0:17:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對了,吃煎餅要喝茶才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.98,0:17:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我的嘴巴也蠻乾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請喝茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.88,0:18:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N差不多該去準備蕎麥麵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.25,0:18:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡看電視就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.85,0:18:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我來這裡打擾妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用這麼介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.83,0:18:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,麵碗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.68,0:18:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拿出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.45,0:18:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請拿麵碗來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.75,0:18:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.52,0:18:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了,這個時候會是誰啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,哪位?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是一之瀨太太啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯的總開關?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.77,0:19:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了,我去看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去一號房看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.84,0:19:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.85,0:19:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,只差一步而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.47,0:19:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩…只剩一步而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.18,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡,我好想做喔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.44,0:20:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請…請問妳聽到什麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.51,0:20:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,聽到一點點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦,我只是想去滑雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很羨慕朱美能去滑雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.76,0:20:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.92,0:20:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.93,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年也留下了很多回憶\N又到了年終
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.54,0:20:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就要走了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.74,0:20:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,蕎麥麵也吃了\N那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.95,0:20:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懷著怎麼樣的心情\N聆聽除夕的鐘聲呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.13,0:21:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有對我做任何不規矩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代真是個紳士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,我想起來了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.01,0:21:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不應該懷疑他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.42,0:22:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,五代不是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.10,0:22:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個千載難逢的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.20,0:22:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我居然敗給了壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.97,0:22:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.41,0:22:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去邀請他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.58,0:22:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該一口氣推倒她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.95,0:22:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.82,0:22:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還醒著嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.43,0:22:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.03,0:22:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在開門的那一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.64,0:22:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我期待她穿著透明睡衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.75,0:23:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去參加跨年參拜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.82,0:23:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我陪妳一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.19,0:23:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是響子不是那種女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.03,0:23:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.43,0:23:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才要請妳多多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.17,0:23:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年你要許什麼願望呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.60,0:23:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛\N希望今年也是個美好的一年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.21,0:23:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.05,0:23:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年我一定要推倒妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.96,0:23:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故鄉應該是在很遠的\N令人用來懷念的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.43,0:23:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是回到故鄉的五代\N卻好像不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.36,0:23:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別以為5號房永遠都在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.80,0:23:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.43,0:24:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「響子焦慮不安?\N五代遲遲未歸之謎」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.77,0:24:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說,你不在身邊\N我就無法展現笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.71,0:24:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天在陌生的城市下了一場陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.65,0:24:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳非常在意淋溼的高跟鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.56,0:24:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前妳用那隱藏著\N稚氣的側臉和我交談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.70,0:24:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的話語至今仍能想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.77,0:25:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就彷佛\N置身電影中的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.45,0:25:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳輕聲細語地說著\N安靜的最後一幕
